description: The BMO MSCI China ESG Leaders Equity Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the MSCI China ESG Leaders Index (Index), net of expenses. The ETF invests in Chinese companies that have higher MSCI ESG ratings than their peers. The ETF invests in and holds the Constituent Securities of the Index in the same proportion as they are reflected in the Index.
name: BMO MSCI China Selection Equity Index ETF
